fields.product_description:
Pure Original Basmati
Visit Tilda.com to find out where our delicious Basmati comes from and for recipe inspiration or contact us via feedback@tilda.com
For full recipes, visit tilda.com/recipes
With half a century of expertise, we hand-select premium grains to make sure only the best rice is used in every Tilda pack. From the foothills of the Himalayas our Pure Basmati Rice is known for its tantalising flavour, magical aroma and delicate, fluffy texture that you'll adore from the very first taste. The perfect companion for a wide range of delicious curries.

fields.product_description:
Apples.
Juicy & Intensely tangy. Hand picked from carefully tended Orchards for a classic, vibrant colour At Tesco we believe in the importance of expertly selecting our seasonal produce for its freshness and quality. Our Granny Smith apples come from trusted growers, predominantly in France and South Africa, where stable temperatures between day and night provide ideal growing conditions. Hand picked for their vibrant, green colour and intensely tangy taste.

fields.product_description:
6 Mixed weight class A organic free range eggs.
From trusted British farms. Our freshly laid eggs come from carefully selected farms. Smaller flocks have plenty of space to roam on organic open pastures from dawn to dusk, and are safely housed in barns overnight. The Lion mark is your guarantee that these are quality eggs laid by British hens vaccinated against Salmonella. See egginfo.co.uk and eggrecipes.co.uk
Fresh from hens on open pastures fed an organic diet.
